GSD.description:
io_uring: calculate CQEs from the user visible value

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.10 by commit 616a725c62e9c42d5073fbd1045832eae64a2ca5, it was introduced in version v5.6 by commit ad3eb2c89fb24d14ac81f43eff8e85fece2c934d. For more details please see the references link.
